name: Do You Like Me? Yes/No/Maybe
description:
The American Autumn's most recent record, released October 2009. Tracks 1,3,5,7 recorded at Red Door Studios in Fox River Grove by Bob Doerr Tracks 2,4,6 recorded at Gravity Studios in Chicago by George Balogi Track 8 recorded at Waysound Studios in Fox River Grove by Justin LeBreck All tracks mastered at Waysound Studios by Justin LeBreck Artwork by Marky Hladish of Midwest Love Art & Design Track Listing
  1. Can't Win 'Em All
  2. North and Damen
  3. This One's For You
  4. You're So Speechless
  5. Bombshells
  6. She Likes The Radio
  7. Farewell June
  8. Sunrise Through Tattered Blinds

name: self titled EP
description: This is The American Autumn’s first release. Recorded December 2007 at Semaphore Studios in Chicago, IL (except for track 4) and mixed at JPL Records in Cary, IL. Track listing 1. Patron Saint 2. Doctor Doctor 3. Flash 4. Bombshells (acoustic)
